com.foreach.across.core

Class DynamicAcrossModuleFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.core.DynamicAcrossModuleFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean<DynamicAcrossModule>

    public class DynamicAcrossModuleFactory
extends Object
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean<DynamicAcrossModule>
    Factory bean that creates a DynamicAcrossModule instance based on a root package and the parameters passed in. If a package is all that is provided, the name of the module will be derived from the lowest package name and all default sub packages will be scanned.

    This class is not thread-safe.

    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
